@startuml
title Flow F-002: Protected API access

actor Client
participant "Security Boundary" as SecurityBoundary
participant "Service Layer" as ServiceLayer
participant "Domain Policy" as DomainPolicy

Client -> SecurityBoundary: Request + access token
SecurityBoundary -> SecurityBoundary: Validate token
SecurityBoundary -> ServiceLayer: Forward caller context
ServiceLayer -> DomainPolicy: Enforce RBAC + object policy
DomainPolicy --> ServiceLayer: Authorization decision
ServiceLayer --> Client: Allow or deny response
@enduml
